@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Film - My Passion";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css">
</head>
<body>

<main>
    <h1>Welcome to My Film Hobby Page:</h1>
    <br>
    <!-- Introductory Sentence with larger font and italics -->
    <p class="intro">Film has been my passion for years. The ability to tell stories through moving images, evoke emotions, and capture imagination is what drives my love for filmmaking.</p>
    
    <!-- Additional Introductory Sentence -->
    <p class="intro">Join me as I explore the world of filmmaking, where creativity and technique come together to create unforgettable stories.</p>

    <br><br>
    
    <!-- Two side-by-side paragraphs -->
    <div class="film-info">
        <div class="paragraph">
            <p>Filmmaking is a unique blend of art and technology. It combines creative storytelling with technical expertise to create something magical on screen. From pre-production planning to post-production editing, every step is crucial to bringing a story to life. The equipment, the crew, and the actors all play essential roles in the process. As a filmmaker, understanding each element and how it contributes to the final product is key to creating a successful film.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="paragraph">
            <p>For me, film is a way to explore different perspectives and emotions. It’s about connecting with people on a deeper level, sharing experiences, and invoking thought. Whether it’s through a documentary or a fictional narrative, film has the power to influence and inspire. Over the years, I’ve learned various techniques and gained invaluable insights into lighting, camera work, and directing. Each project teaches me something new, and that’s what makes filmmaking so exciting.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h1>Here are some images of me enjoying my hobby:</h1>
    <br>
    <!-- Photos next to each other -->
    <div class="film-images">
        <img src="~/images/guywatchingmovie.jpg" alt="Filmmaking Sample 1">
        <img src="~/images/friendswatchingmovie.jpeg" alt="Filmmaking Sample 2">
    </div>

</main>

</body>
</html>
